<figureCitation box="[743,845,1309,1335]" captionStart-0="Fig" captionStart-1="Fig" captionStartId-0="5.[189,232,1855,1881]" captionStartId-1="6.[189,232,1431,1457]" captionTargetBox-0="[232,1344,267,1821]" captionTargetBox-1="[195,1395,268,1391]" captionTargetId-0="figure-99@5.[227,1361,259,1847]" captionTargetId-1="figure-150@6.[189,1398,265,1394]" captionTargetPageId-0="5" captionTargetPageId-1="6" captionText-0="Fig. 1. Andes balteiformis Wang, Zhi &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♂. A. Dorsal view. B. Lateral view. C. Head and thorax, dorsal view. D. Face, ventral view. E. Forewing. F. Genitalia, lateral view. G. Pygofer and gonostyli, ventral view. H. Anal segment, dorsal view. I. Gonostyli, lateral view. J. Aedeagus, right side. K. Aedeagus, left side. L. Aedeagus, dorsal view. M. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bars: A–D, F–M = 0.5 mm; E = 1.0 mm." captionText-1="Fig. 2. Andes balteiformis Wang, Zhi &amp; Chen sp. nOv., ♀. A. Genitalia, lateral view. B. Genitalia, ventral view. C. Anal segment, dorsal view. D. Tergite IX, caudal view. E. Gonapophysis VIII and gonocoxa VIII, dorsal view. F. Gonapophysis IX, lateral view. G. Gonoplac, inner lateral view. H. Posterior vagina, ventral view. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862169" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6862173" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/6862169/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/6862173/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="48">Figs 1–2</figureCitation>
